# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok spain 's inditex , europe 's largest clothing retailer , said wednesday it would start selling its flagship zara brand clothes over the internet later this year in selected european markets .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (c / company
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Inditex")
            :poss (c2 / company
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Spain"))
            :mod (c3 / clothing)
            :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (l / large)
                  :ARG3 (m / most)
                  :ARG5 (r / retailer
                        :mod (c4 / clothing)
                        :location (c5 / continent
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Europe")))))
      :ARG1 (s2 / start-01
            :ARG0 c
            :ARG1 (s3 / sell-01
                  :ARG0 c
                  :ARG1 (c6 / clothes
                        :ARG1-of (b / brand-01
                              :ARG2 (p / product
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Zara")))
                        :mod (f / flagship))
                  :ARG2 (m2 / market
                        :ARG1-of (s4 / select-01)
                        :mod c5)
                  :time (a / after
                        :op1 (n5 / now))
                  :medium (ii / internet)
                  :time (y / year
                        :mod (t / this))))
      :time (w / wednesday))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a new test that can detect several kinds of cancerous human cells was reported yesterday by scientists from the johns hopkins school of medicine in baltimore .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (s / scientist
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (s2 / school
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Johns"
                              :op2 "Hopkins"
                              :op3 "School"
                              :op4 "of"
                              :op5 "Medicine")
                        :location (c / city
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Baltimore")))))
      :ARG1 (t / test-01
            :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)
            :ARG0-of (d / detect-01
                  :ARG1 (c2 / cell
                        :mod (h2 / human)
                        :mod (k / kind
                              :quant (s3 / several)))
                  :ARG1-of (p / possible-01)))
      :time (y / yesterday))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok american diplomats met tuesday night with the crew of a fallen u.s. spy plane , nearly three days after it made an emergency landing at a chinese military base after colliding with a chinese fighter jet .
# ::alignments
(m / meet-03
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "America"))
                  :ARG2 (d / diplomat)))
      :ARG1 (p2 / person
            :ARG0-of (c2 / crew-01
                  :ARG1 (p3 / plane
                        :mod (s / spy-01)
                        :mod (c3 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "U.S."))
                        :ARG1-of (f / fall-05))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)
            :dayperiod (n3 / night))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (l / land-01
                  :ARG1 p3
                  :mod (e / emergency)
                  :location (b / base
                        :mod (m2 / military)
                        :mod (c4 / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "China")))
                  :time (a2 / after
                        :op1 (c5 / collide-01
                              :ARG1 p3
                              :ARG2 (j / jet
                                    :ARG0-of (f2 / fight-01)
                                    :mod c4))))
            :quant (n5 / nearly
                  :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 3
                        :unit (d3 / day)))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok oversize posters of president hamid karzai blanketed the afghan capital tuesday as the two-month presidential campaign began .

(b / blanket-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (p2 / post-01
                  :ARG2 (p3 / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Hamid"
                              :op2 "Karzai")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Afghanistan"))
                              :ARG2 (p4 / president)))))
      :ARG1 (c2 / city
            :ARG0-of h
            :ARG1 c
            :ARG2 (c3 / capital))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday))
      :time (b2 / begin-01
            :ARG1 (c4 / campaign
                  :mod p4
                  :duration (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 2
                        :unit (m / month)))))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

(w / win-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Marie-gaianeh"
                  :op2 "Mikaelian")
            :mod (s / seed
                  :mod (t / top)))
      :ARG1 (t2 / title
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1)
            :part-of (c / career
                  :poss p))
      :ARG4 (e / event
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 " ###,###"
                  :op2 " dollars"))
      :location (h / here)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s2 / sunday)))

      :ARG1 (s2 / succeed-01
            :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                  :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01
                        :ARG1 (c3 / county
                              :part (c4 / center))))
            :ARG1 (g3 / gain-02
                  :ARG0 g
                  :ARG1 (a / access-01
                        :ARG0 g
                        :ARG1 (m / market
                              :mod (p2 / province
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Macau"))
                              :purpose (g4 / good
                                    :mod (a2 / agriculture)
                                    :poss c3))))
            :time (r / recent))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))

                  :op2 "Pealand"))

            :ARG0 p

                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Zimbabwe"))

                  :weekday (t3 / thursday))
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 2))
      :time (p2 / prepare-02
            :ARG0 (s3 / side
                  :mod (b / both))
            :ARG2 (w / wicket
                  :ARG0-of (t4 / turn-01))))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok russia is cautiously optimistic that the crew of a russian cargo helicopter seized by sudanese authorities on its way to congo would soon be released , the foreign ministry spokesman said friday .

      :ARG0 (p / person

                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Foreign"
                              :op2 "Ministry"))
                  :ARG2 (s2 / spokesman)))
      :ARG1 (o / optimistic
            :domain (c / country
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Russia"))
            :topic (r / release-01
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG0-of (c2 / crew-01
                        :ARG1 (h2 / helicopter
                              :mod (c3 / cargo)
                              :mod c
                              :ARG1-of (s3 / seize-01
                                    :ARG0 (a / authority
                                          :mod (c4 / country
                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Saudi"
                                                      :op2 "Arabia")))
                                    :purpose (g2 / go-02
                                          :ARG0 h2
                                          :ARG4 (h3 / home))))))
            :time (s4 / soon))
      :manner (c5 / cautious)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday)))

                              :mod (f / female)

                                    :ARG2 (g / great)
                                    :ARG3 (m2 / most))))))
      :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
            :ARG0 (t / try-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (w / win-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG2 (m3 / marathon
                              :location (c2 / city
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "New"
                                          :op2 "York"))

                                    :value 4)

                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Nov."))))))

# ::id 9 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :name (n / name

                  :op2 "Mercantile"
                  :op3 "Exchange")

                  :mod (f / finance)

                        :ARG2 (l / large)
                        :ARG3 (m / most)
                        :ARG5 (e3 / exchange
                              :location (w / world)))))
      :ARG1 (a2 / and
            :op1 (e4 / expand-01
                  :ARG0 e
                  :ARG1 (d / derivative
                        :mod (w2 / weather)))
            :op2 (r / roll-out-02
                  :ARG0 e
                  :ARG1 (a3 / and
                        :op1 (f2 / futures
                              :mod (ii / index
                                    :mod (w3 / weather))
                              :frequency (r2 / rate-entity-91
                                    :ARG3 (t / temporal-quantity
                                          :quant 1
                                          :unit (w4 / week))))
                        :op2 (o / option
                              :mod (f3 / futures)
                              :location (c / city
                                    :location (c2 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "United"
                                                :op2 "States")))))
                  :ARG1-of (b / begin-01
                        :time (d2 / date-entity
                              :month 4
                              :time-of a2)))
            :weekday (m2 / monday)))

# ::id 20 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

      :op1 (s / swoop-01
            :ARG0 (p / person

            :ARG1 (u / underbrush
                  :location (a2 / along

                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Acadia"
                                          :op2 "National"
                                          :op3 "Park")
                                    :location (c / city
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Maine"))))))
            :manner (g / good-02))
      :op2 (e / emerge-01
            :ARG0 p
            :manner (t2 / triumph-01)
            :manner (c2 / cradle-01
                  :ARG0 (g2 / grasshopper
                        :part h
                        :mod (l / leg
